OL,3,COne man in hospital and two people
OL,4,Carrested after serious assault
OL,6,FTwo people have been arrested and one
OL,7,Fman is in hospital after what police
OL,8,Fhave described as a serious assault in
OL,9,FBristol.
OL,11,FAvon and Somerset Police were called
OL,12,Fto an address Whitchurch shortly
OL,13,Fbefore 11pm on Saturday 28 March.
OL,15,FA man in his sixties was found wounded
OL,16,Finside the property and was taken to
OL,17,Fhospital.
OL,19,FA woman in her sixties and a man in
OL,20,Fhis thirties were arrested and are in
OL,21,Fpolice custody.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
